Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.90,0:01:36.70,qianxu-title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,700)\bord0.1\shad8\blur6\4c&H6E61CD&\pos(1414.533,897.6)}轉變形象的千緒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.85,0:01:35.44,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都高中了依舊是臨時抱佛腳？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.73,0:01:39.15,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\an7}註：左邊海報的梗是《生化奇兵：無限》(Bioshock: Infinite)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.63,0:01:38.88,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 這可是我出色的考試對策
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.21,0:01:40.64,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給 這是夜宵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.62,0:01:42.62,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那你好好努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.83,0:01:52.19,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs65}註：此處海報的梗是《半條命》(Half Life)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.14,0:01:48.52,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為文科只要背就行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.60,0:01:52.19,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,努力一晚應該能拿到中下等的分數
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.42,0:01:59.22,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？「典拠」的「拠」字怎麼寫來著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.29,0:02:06.04,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我只記到那裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.72,0:02:09.24,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,回過神來發現不知為何自己在玩槍戰網遊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.62,0:02:11.68,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,突然被打中不小心叫出聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.70,0:02:14.40,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後我媽就衝進來罵我最後兩人吵了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.74,0:02:17.08,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一氣之下躺床上睡覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.67,0:02:21.66,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你完全沒複習今天的考試？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.34,0:02:22.84,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.20,0:02:26.32,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是呀 我有最後的最後的對策
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.37,0:02:29.96,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對策…別跟我說是求神保佑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.52,0:02:31.96,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,神明保佑神明保佑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.05,0:02:34.20,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,求神明保佑！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.14,0:02:41.36,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 這樣應該沒問題了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.67,0:02:44.22,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟 我放了100日元香油錢進去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.58,0:02:46.48,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣考試應該沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.92,0:02:49.28,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,從而我的人生也能平平安安了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.43,0:02:50.84,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你真樂觀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.16,0:02:53.60,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得神明會答應你這麼好的要求？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.72,0:02:56.80,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個請求 老夫答應了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.60,0:02:58.80,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誰…是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.33,0:03:04.78,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs65}註：權現為佛教用語。表示佛、菩薩為普渡眾生而顯現化身。權字表示「臨時」之意。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.33,0:03:04.78,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老夫 大權現
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.99,0:03:08.26,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是！跟久志取前輩一起在公園的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.72,0:03:09.44,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.54,0:03:11.02,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,許久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.26,0:03:13.04,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,話說他在這幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.51,0:03:14.12,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三谷裳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.93,0:03:15.98,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他記得我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.08,0:03:18.52,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你似乎在為考試的事情煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.58,0:03:23.30,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,女子高中生的名字老夫只要聽過一遍就絕不會忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.30,0:03:25.86,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,絕不會！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.94,0:03:27.13,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.78,0:03:31.38,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老夫想給你個建議
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.07,0:03:35.48,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別看老夫這樣 以前也是被稱為「精英」的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.11,0:03:38.17,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是學歷社會的贏家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.89,0:03:41.54,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}對這個社會的運作可謂了如指掌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.04,0:03:42.66,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來他以前說過自己是能幹的上班族
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.81,0:03:46.20,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,歸根結底 區區讀書之事 何必為之盡心盡力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.45,0:03:47.70,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.96,0:03:52.44,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs60}註：偏差值類似於國內的標準分，學力偏差值用來表示學生在所屬群體裡的學力排名情況，\N越高越好。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.96,0:03:52.44,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了 諸位女子與其提高學力偏差值
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.52,0:03:55.00,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,更應當提高外貌偏差值！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.10,0:03:56.88,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,斷言了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.93,0:04:00.92,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了 老夫打從在公司工作開始就一直看過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:07.80,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人事部在招聘女生時相比學歷更多是只看容姿來決定是否採用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.29,0:04:09.73,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,於是呢三谷裳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.46,0:04:12.83,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我來重新把你改造吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.69,0:04:15.69,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's 擅於處世吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.34,0:04:20.82,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 確實長得漂亮可能在各方面都會有利
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.36,0:04:24.22,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那種果然還是需要底子好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.74,0:04:27.38,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且不可愛的孩子勉強努力的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.51,0:04:31.04,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺會被盯上 遇上不好的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:34.06,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,像我這種中下等的女生…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.19,0:04:35.16,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.14,0:04:42.64,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你很美 毫無疑問是鑽石的原石
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.37,0:04:45.48,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老夫想親自為你打磨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.42,0:04:48.32,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真奈菜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.23,0:04:55.94,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒有發覺嗎 我也一直是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.50,0:04:58.22,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要被改造！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.25,0:05:01.26,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,事情變得有趣起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.07,0:05:03.83,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs90\an8}千緒美人化作戰開始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.90,0:05:08.86,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼一來你的人生也變成簡單模式了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.02,0:05:10.36,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.78,0:05:12.34,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也幫幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.46,0:05:13.50,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.67,0:05:16.24,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過這些假髮是哪來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.57,0:05:21.04,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,實際上這家神社的地板下面是我撿的廢品的倉庫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.24,0:05:22.34,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會遭天譴的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:27.00,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 先讓我看看三谷裳現在的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.49,0:05:29.06,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能摘掉眼鏡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.40,0:05:30.30,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.12,0:05:34.96,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,臉好平淡！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.78,0:05:38.87,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說實話我是帶著半開玩笑的心態開始的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.08,0:05:41.28,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這看來會是件苦活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.46,0:05:45.04,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼說呢 像是白開水的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.44,0:05:48.92,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 這素顏依舊讓人覺得眼鏡才是你的本體
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.71,0:05:52.56,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說如此 眼鏡能增加純粹的陰鬱感
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.64,0:05:54.52,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}要摘掉的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.99,0:05:54.64,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺跟剛才說的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.17,0:05:57.60,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為了能夠改造這個土裡土氣的髮型
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.68,0:06:00.56,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,首先戴上長髮假髮看看情況
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:05.68,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不就是個家裡蹲了3年的網遊廢人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.86,0:06:09.54,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,長髮也像某某閣下一樣挺合適的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.86,0:06:09.54,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs65}註：「ムッシュ」為法語「閣下」，此處梗為Monsieur Kamayatsu，是已故日本搖\N滾音樂人，本名為釜萢弘。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.54,0:06:11.94,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}是嗎 不過那是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.16,0:06:12.08,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,假髮髮質太差了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.08,0:06:14.00,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微剪一剪整理一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.32,0:06:16.22,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聲音不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.64,0:06:18.72,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那手法 真是嫻熟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.96,0:06:21.10,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這位老爺爺 果然絕非常人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.77,0:06:26.38,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,品味真昭和！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.52,0:06:32.12,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 難得那個偏保守的小千緒樂觀對待形象打扮…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.46,0:06:34.42,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,化妝就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.48,0:06:35.14,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.68,0:06:40.50,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs65}註：「現充」指現實(real)生活中充實的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.68,0:06:40.50,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也會竭盡全力 帶你走向現充之路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.71,0:06:46.92,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真奈真奈真奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.10,0:06:49.56,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這是何等的身法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.87,0:06:50.79,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,目標是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.88,0:06:53.84,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,時下流行的 大眼妝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.08,0:06:57.08,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.08,0:06:57.08,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs65}註：「それな」為日本流行語，表示贊同、附和。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.56,0:06:58.22,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.04,0:07:02.26,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,凝聚了我技術的精華
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:05.42,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.10,0:07:07.08,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:17.78,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是完全的失敗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:20.30,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事啊那奇怪的髮型
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.36,0:07:23.76,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我哪知道摘了眼鏡後臉會變得那麼樸素
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.93,0:07:26.36,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以想著至少髮型要華麗一點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:29.86,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在小千緒想照鏡子 躍躍欲試 你說怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.94,0:07:32.18,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說到底你才是怎麼回事 那種化妝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.21,0:07:35.66,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我哪有辦法 做了各種實驗之後就起興了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.81,0:07:39.08,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明知故犯？你這也算是朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.09,0:07:41.24,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒誒 商量完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.18,0:07:46.20,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,首先得想辦法處理一下那個可悲的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.32,0:07:47.38,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也…也對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.09,0:07:49.66,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 要重新改造嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.78,0:07:51.98,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎麼說時間還是不夠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.82,0:07:56.44,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說到底戴上金髮的那個瞬間我就覺得有點不對了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:07:58.58,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.02,0:08:01.20,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小千緒她 該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.25,0:08:02.34,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,臉長得很過時呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.21,0:08:07.08,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以化妝的時候不管怎樣都會一不留神做過頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.36,0:08:07.89,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:10.76,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,乾脆把那個馬面給她戴上逃走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.04,0:08:13.06,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我在學校還會見到她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.86,0:08:17.06,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果用這個的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.13,0:08:18.34,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 確實
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.96,0:08:21.48,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,憑那傢伙平淡的臉的話 說不定能行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:24.48,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小千緒 之前的都不算
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.62,0:08:26.22,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後把這個也這樣弄的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.98,0:08:30.48,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.98,0:08:30.48,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs65}註：此處為配合日式髮型說出的「どすえ」是日本京都腔獨有的句尾，相當於「ですよ」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.16,0:08:32.24,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好合適
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.38,0:08:34.02,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,終 終於找到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.12,0:08:36.00,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最適合你的髮型
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:38.04,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,竟 竟然這麼合適
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:39.98,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼我之前都沒注意到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.22,0:08:41.28,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 這麼合適嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:43.26,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,改變形象成功了的感覺？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.32,0:08:44.62,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.16,0:08:46.18,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有違和感之類的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.31,0:08:48.18,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 令人畏懼般地沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.73,0:08:52.40,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,性 性感度也…好好地表露出來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.91,0:08:54.92,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.08,0:08:56.68,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}有男生也會喜歡的感覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:08:56.58,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼一說本來是這樣的主旨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.19,0:09:00.64,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…那個…說實話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.08,0:09:03.16,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是會出黃書的等級
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.50,0:09:05.92,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然到達這種次元了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.10,0:09:07.70,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 你那什麼表達方式啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.80,0:09:10.58,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不 日本畫的美女都是那種感覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.60,0:09:13.46,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.66,0:09:17.14,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和水手服絕望般的不搭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.30,0:09:20.70,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 但是 這種模式的故事也經常有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.91,0:09:22.36,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 兩位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:24.80,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.22,0:09:32.18,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,從今天起中下的女孩也…終於畢業了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.67,0:09:34.33,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,從今以後把男孩的心…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.39,0:09:37.40,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不斷地變成我的俘虜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.25,0:09:39.60,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 兩位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.40,0:09:43.56,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,重生的性感小千緒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.38,0:09:45.18,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.84,0:10:22.06,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（字幕組聽不懂日式英語）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.16,0:10:32.66,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:35.60,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個壓倒性的性感的鋼管舞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.82,0:10:36.74,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.80,0:10:37.58,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.72,0:10:40.34,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和新生小千緒的誕生相符的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.42,0:10:45.84,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 這和平常的髮型…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.23,0:10:46.94,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真奈菜？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.13,0:10:47.45,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.70,0:10:50.92,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,實際上 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.97,0:10:52.20,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 是的 是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.56,0:10:53.76,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.29,0:10:57.44,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小千緒像個中下等一樣的 本來的姿態
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.82,0:11:01.38,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是最高貴 最美麗的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.31,0:11:05.07,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那會出黃書的等級是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.35,0:11:06.28,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.40,0:11:08.42,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即使總的來說不是主流
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.50,0:11:11.82,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在某處也肯定會有需求的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.04,0:11:14.16,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.21,0:11:16.58,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.79,0:11:19.46,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是浪費時間啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.59,0:11:21.02,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我去上學了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.17,0:11:22.20,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.28,0:11:24.34,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}我不及格了就是你們倆的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.04,0:11:25.34,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.87,0:11:29.18,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又一大早開始就能和JK一起玩真是開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.32,0:11:31.20,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:34.38,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一點希望你們記住
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.43,0:11:37.34,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能用假髮來玩耍的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.86,0:11:43.06,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有並不真正需要它的幸福的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.62,0:11:46.62,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千緒的神明保佑…通學…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.68,0:11:48.04,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鋼管舞什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.24,0:11:49.75,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你什麼時候學會的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.36,0:11:53.86,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 好像遊戲裡有個色情酒吧一樣的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.26,0:11:55.42,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為感覺挺閒的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.45,0:11:56.96,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就看了一整天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.76,0:11:59.04,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後就自然地學會了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.66,0:12:00.32,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.76,0:12:02.22,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作為女孩子的話已經完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.87,0:12:14.33,qianxu-title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(900,600)\bord0.1\shad8\blur6\4c&H6E61CD&\pos(1521.2,884.267)}Flat Cut
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.87,0:12:14.33,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an7\fs65}註：Flat Cut是一種剪雪茄的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.19,0:12:11.56,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.13,0:12:13.78,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,河上的水管
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.96,0:12:14.68,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.59,0:12:18.36,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡棒？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.68,0:12:20.86,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個柵欄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.06,0:12:22.46,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個光滑的立足點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.85,0:12:26.68,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明怎麼看都做成了對想走過去的人很苛刻的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.84,0:12:28.66,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}不 這個不能走過去的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.38,0:12:29.78,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是正中間卻好好地有著休息處
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.37,0:12:31.98,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那個不是休息處啊　
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.62,0:12:34.18,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然很強很苛刻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.58,0:12:37.14,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但在那之中也像飽含著溫柔的男人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.59,0:12:38.18,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.62,0:12:39.44,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小千緒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.52,0:12:42.30,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不 完全不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.47,0:12:45.22,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不如說把橋擬人就像個腐女一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.27,0:12:47.10,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誰是腐女啊 我靠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.78,0:12:47.50,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.58,0:12:48.38,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不 因為
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.42,0:12:51.50,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道小千緒你房間有BL遊戲的書啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.79,0:12:55.30,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好像就這一塊隆起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.86,0:12:59.74,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那個是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.78,0:13:01.36,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是搞錯了才買的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.54,0:13:03.60,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,偶爾拿出來看一下而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.36,0:13:05.68,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個話題已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.96,0:13:08.86,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想談論那個水管的帥氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.99,0:13:11.94,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說 普通的女生是不會對那個有感覺的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.50,0:13:15.62,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼想都很帥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.72,0:13:17.42,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}結婚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.50,0:13:18.88,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在那個上面 被求婚的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.99,0:13:20.58,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是一不留神就會說OK的程度的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.00,0:13:24.48,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明都沒有男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.80,0:13:25.72,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卻從小千緒嘴裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.66,0:13:26.34,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}求…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.89,0:13:26.75,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.78,0:13:28.36,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒什麼問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.50,0:13:29.43,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.48,0:13:30.32,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.42,0:13:31.18,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}夠了 夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.28,0:13:32.98,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 剛才真有意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.28,0:13:36.72,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是有點不明白小千緒的帥氣的標準啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.39,0:13:40.10,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的話不管過多久戀人什麼的都不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.64,0:13:41.36,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.18,0:13:46.86,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 安藤先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.49,0:13:48.54,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,報紙？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.84,0:13:53.51,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,安藤流
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.91,0:13:55.78,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,配送報紙術奧義
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.22,0:13:57.48,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,破天！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.32,0:14:02.76,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.39,0:14:06.34,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 怎麼了你們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.63,0:14:11.14,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好像我鼓足幹勁的時候被看到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.61,0:14:13.26,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過因為是最後的一個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.38,0:14:14.58,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一不小心就… 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.72,0:14:17.66,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那個完全就是在顯擺吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.76,0:14:21.26,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好 好厲害好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.72,0:14:21.36,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}小千緒？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:22.40,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才的是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.52,0:14:23.02,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是…哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.30,0:14:23.86,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小千緒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.12,0:14:26.36,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完全上鈎並且嗨起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.95,0:14:29.24,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果這就是安藤先生的目的的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.59,0:14:30.82,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.24,0:14:34.30,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,安藤先生喜歡千緒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.90,0:14:35.23,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.02,0:14:41.90,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺好像很輕易地就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.28,0:14:45.86,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？我會錯意了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.34,0:14:47.84,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,安藤先生只是純粹…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.58,0:14:53.74,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,既然一份工作做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.12,0:14:55.44,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來就吸一根吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.89,0:14:59.40,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 話說我已經戒了這玩意兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.16,0:15:01.84,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是自言自語吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.79,0:15:04.50,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是要雪茄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.22,0:15:07.68,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,掏出了更顯擺的傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.34,0:15:19.72,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不 雖然很相稱…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.22,0:15:23.18,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 三谷裳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.22,0:15:24.32,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 就是雪茄嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.38,0:15:25.10,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.18,0:15:26.44,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.49,0:15:27.80,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就確定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.17,0:15:32.40,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,安藤先生的行動都是 對小千緒的自我展示
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.67,0:15:33.41,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.55,0:15:36.22,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,安藤先生喜歡小千緒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.30,0:15:36.96,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,並且
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.08,0:15:39.18,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,安藤先生的有點方向不對的自我展示
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.28,0:15:42.08,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,非常戳中小千緒的點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.32,0:15:43.36,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個搞不好的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.46,0:15:44.60,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,配對成功？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.29,0:15:47.18,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然小千緒好像沒有注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.44,0:15:49.46,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個組合怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.14,0:15:51.98,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為和小千緒交往的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.18,0:15:55.28,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是這幅畫裡這種樣子的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.94,0:15:57.92,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然安藤先生沒有學歷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.05,0:15:59.40,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過那種類型恐怖的是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.32,0:16:01.90,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一發逆轉一夜暴富
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.80,0:16:05.56,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來混混的天生的行動力以及為人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.74,0:16:08.58,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出了社會的話就成功地出人頭地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:11.98,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事也有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:09.98,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}放馬過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.46,0:16:13.42,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想像一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.80,0:16:15.20,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,應當到來的未來…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.00,0:16:18.76,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,蔬菜的價格又漲了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.08,0:16:21.28,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,水在這裡買也很重
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.65,0:16:23.90,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,至少能買輛小汽車的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.46,0:16:26.30,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敞篷車？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.13,0:16:28.80,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在這種有點冷的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.14,0:16:30.76,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小千緒？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.93,0:16:32.00,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 這不是真奈菜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.12,0:16:35.10,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你又買了新車嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.16,0:16:36.72,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.80,0:16:40.44,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭 都是老公說要在這種時候坐敞篷車
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.51,0:16:42.50,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是笨蛋呢 我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.68,0:16:45.60,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過也因此買了大衣就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.86,0:16:48.26,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真奈菜你的自行車是因為那個叫「健康志向」的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.86,0:16:50.36,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.42,0:16:51.92,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.00,0:16:54.24,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真奈菜也要買車的話外國車也不錯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.36,0:16:56.70,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}這…這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.38,0:16:56.48,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然日元匯率低車又比較貴就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.94,0:16:59.74,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過買這種方向盤靠左的車
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.82,0:17:01.60,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在停車場就很困擾了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.70,0:17:06.12,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 給停車卡的機器只有右邊有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.13,0:17:08.72,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過城市的超市倒是兩邊都有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.14,0:17:10.78,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.33,0:17:14.86,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,盯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.02,0:17:23.13,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等下 突然間怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.31,0:17:26.34,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你衣服上有很多小蟲子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.49,0:17:27.70,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別殺了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.85,0:17:29.48,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}為什麼 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.09,0:17:29.78,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,思考下 好好思考下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.96,0:17:31.52,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後採取對策
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.92,0:17:35.14,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為了千緒「中下等」的幸福未來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.10,0:17:38.88,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在這前面安藤先生一定也做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.41,0:17:41.14,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,安藤先生會做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.34,0:17:44.16,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}小姐姐 要不要喝杯茶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.17,0:17:45.18,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}黑髮那位挺可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.23,0:17:46.62,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}比起右邊那位還是左邊好點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.42,0:17:46.54,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託同伴把我們包圍起來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.90,0:17:47.60,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.93,0:17:49.96,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧三谷裳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.05,0:17:50.72,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.40,0:17:54.46,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不 怎麼說那個人也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.71,0:17:57.44,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.22,0:17:59.66,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吃這麼急
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.50,0:18:01.16,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.11,0:18:03.62,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可能只是個單純的傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.51,0:18:06.86,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不 本來應該是這樣才對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.13,0:18:11.24,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為那把多餘的傘全部的計劃的暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.86,0:18:13.06,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千緒的反應是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.06,0:18:16.58,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 那隻貓是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.68,0:18:17.42,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喬治
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.64,0:18:19.24,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,安藤先生 那隻貓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.83,0:18:20.98,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.22,0:18:29.02,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好 下一手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.22,0:18:30.86,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說了下一手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.80,0:18:35.30,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺好像放著不管也沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.78,0:18:41.53,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定安藤先生是不是…喜歡我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.00,0:18:45.74,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.91,0:18:48.84,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像郵件什麼的偶爾也會發過來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.14,0:18:49.07,qianxu-huamian3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs50\fad(300,0)\frz15.07\c&H43423B&\b1\pos(420,638)}因為明天很熱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.14,0:18:49.07,qianxu-huamian3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs50\fad(300,0)\frz14.53\pos(564,662)\c&H43423B&\b1}所以雪糕應該會挺好吃的。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.14,0:18:49.07,qianxu-huamian3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs50\fad(300,0)\frz14.5\c&H43423B&\b1\pos(536,728)}牧場的那家真好吃啊。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.25,0:18:51.54,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼時候給了郵件地址…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.78,0:18:56.28,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道已經有那種關係 在我不知道的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.48,0:18:57.82,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.31,0:18:57.82,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}真奈菜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.18,0:19:00.16,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕的話說不定在這條上學路上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.27,0:19:02.86,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小千緒真的會被攻略
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.89,0:19:04.54,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,影子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.93,0:19:05.94,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是安藤先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.43,0:19:07.84,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這回又是什麼手段
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.10,0:19:22.66,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這 這下成了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.97,0:19:28.34,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在便利店打工的時候偶然知道了三谷裳的BL愛好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.12,0:19:30.68,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,從那以後一直在玩遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.82,0:19:32.84,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也在網上看了很多學習了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.62,0:19:35.50,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三谷裳的話應該是明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.76,0:19:38.36,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我愛你 翔平
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.52,0:19:39.82,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.17,0:19:42.72,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,超有名BL遊戲「安德爾」的名場景
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.87,0:19:44.52,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,通稱「腳咚」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.89,0:19:45.70,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.88,0:19:47.38,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了後輩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.14,0:19:49.70,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我只能拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.84,0:19:52.50,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是為了安藤大哥的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.98,0:19:54.74,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真…真的要上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.80,0:19:57.24,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 全體重加上來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.87,0:20:03.40,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的 只要越過這個的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.22,0:20:06.88,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 這不是「安德爾」的「腳咚」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.00,0:20:09.04,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,安藤先生你很懂BL嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.06,0:20:10.68,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}有空一起聊聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.14,0:20:10.76,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她的…笑容…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.94,0:20:18.34,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.03,0:20:21.72,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,注意到啊 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.68,0:20:25.24,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真奈菜 那是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.51,0:20:30.44,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,介紹下 這是我男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.04,0:20:34.28,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為很恩愛所以給你們看看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.69,0:20:37.08,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,順便 我的身體很柔軟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.82,0:20:38.66,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.95,0:20:40.72,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不如說只能這麼認為
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.29,0:20:42.96,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那不打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.16,0:20:44.06,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們就先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.94,0:20:45.98,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦！？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.30,0:20:49.00,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是「安德爾」的那個誒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.92,0:20:54.58,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一大早就看了好不得了的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.09,0:20:58.20,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,目的地是相同的 也是為了見戀人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.75,0:21:01.96,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千緒你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.27,0:21:07.74,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不 安藤先生對我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.68,0:21:11.44,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說了這麼害羞的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.18,0:21:16.34,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明不可能有人喜歡我的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.65,0:21:18.62,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒這種事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.70,0:21:20.88,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啦沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.98,0:21:22.64,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.24,0:21:25.04,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒這種事 哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.78,0:21:29.60,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 明明到途中還是很順利的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.92,0:21:30.66,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.87,0:21:32.12,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也對不起你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.48,0:21:34.00,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你做了奇怪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.21,0:21:37.92,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不是很介意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.38,0:21:42.51,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千緒的通學路 咚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.37,0:21:46.02,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到手了 三谷裳的郵件地址
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.78,0:21:48.76,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天一定要約她出來約會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.35,0:21:51.42,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能太直接要有適度的距離感
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.88,0:21:53.04,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不是很懂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.12,0:21:54.08,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎…
