Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.95,0:21:54.09,qianxu-title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60\bord0\c&H686665&\frz19.83\pos(1396,264)\b0}因為明天很熱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.95,0:21:54.09,qianxu-title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz19.83\fs60\bord0\c&H686665&\pos(1574,274)\b0}所以雪糕應該會挺好吃的。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.95,0:21:54.09,qianxu-title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\b0\frz19.83\fs60\bord0\c&H686665&\pos(1546,356)}牧場的那家真好吃啊。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.60,0:21:55.70,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,考慮性價比的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.82,0:21:58.74,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢啃冰凍的果汁也不錯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.28,0:22:00.54,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被甩了
Comment: 0,0:22:01.19,0:23:29.22,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,----ed----
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.36,0:23:33.20,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下回的千緒的通學路是由
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.28,0:23:36.12,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「篠塜和糖分和記者招待會」「Thousand Spring」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.16,0:23:38.14,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和「安藤與喬治」三部分組成
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.15,0:23:38.92,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敬請期待
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.96,0:23:40.50,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,糖分目前等分
