Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.16,0:22:35.35,qianxu_EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\fad(10,300)}雖然是理所當然的見面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.58,0:22:38.66,qianxu_EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\fad(10,300)}但是每天卻非常開心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.95,0:22:45.32,qianxu_EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\fad(10,300)}歡笑的時候 生氣的時候 都想全力碰撞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.36,0:22:51.13,qianxu_EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\fad(10,300)}不想說再見的感覺是想要隱藏起來的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.51,0:22:57.30,qianxu_EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\fad(10,300)}在回家之前就是上學哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.92,0:22:59.51,qianxu_EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\fad(10,300)}明天再見哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.54,0:23:04.33,qianxu_EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\fad(10,300)}不是你的話不就開始不了不是嗎 你說對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.67,0:23:10.75,qianxu_EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\fad(10,300)}無法見面的時間 為什麼總是感覺有所欠缺
